OL,5, Former minister Derek MacKay said he   
OL,6, takes his share of responsibility for  
OL,7, the failure to deliver two ferries for 
OL,8, Calmac's west coast routes.            
OL,10,FThe former MSP was speaking to         
OL,11,FHolyrood's Public Audit Committee which
OL,12,Fis looking at why the vessels are years
OL,13,Flate and over budget.                  
OL,15,FHe denied that the contract was awarded
OL,16,Fto Port Glasgow-based Ferguson shipyard
OL,17,Ffor political reasons.                 
OL,19,FMr Mackay resigned in 2020 amid a      
OL,20,Fscandal over messages to a teenage boy.
